    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> soft cheese</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong>,<strong> </strong>1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>boiled water</strong>, and season with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>soft cheese mix</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p>",
